paragraph.content:
for the transfer to the High Court of any cause or proceedings upon
                            the application of any party or at the instance of the District Court;
                            and

subsection.def:
*commencement date (生效日期) means the date on which the Interest and
                Surcharge on Arrears of Maintenance Ordinance 2003 (18 of
                    2003) comes into operation;

paragraph.content:
if there are any proceedings instituted for enforcing the maintenance
                    order, the costs ordered by the court to be paid under those
                    proceedings;

the judgment debtor’s past record and conduct in connection with the making
                    of maintenance payments to the judgment creditor pursuant to the maintenance
                    order or an undertaking in any proceedings;
